-- #### 1.3 Other methods for Table Population/ Creation
-- The following methods are all quite useful for table creation (plus data population from an existing table): 
-- - INSERT INTO 
-- - SELECT INTO FROM 
-- - CREATE TABLE AS SELECT 
-- 
-- You must have a pre-existing table (or tables) in Fabric somewhere, Lakehouse (hook into the T-SQL Endpoint) or Data Warehouse.
