-- #### 3.2 Implementing Slowly-Changing Dimensions
-- 
-- Please note, this is a condensed version of the SCD tutorials in Fabric Dojo - for the full explanations, make sure you complete the following exercises: 
-- - [DW025 🟢 DM Concepts 4: SCDs](https://www.skool.com/fabricdojo/classroom/4958d998?md=858e345702c1407daa4341e45f94c978)
